content: The girls all smiled as they watched Lizzie sleep, feeling content and satisfied with their ticklish fun. Lumina and Nara went back to their own things, while Zara continued to softly pet Lizzie's foot. Alyssa looked down at Lizzie, feeling grateful for having such a cute and loving girlfriend. She leaned down and placed a gentle kiss on Lizzie's forehead, before also going back to her own activities. The girls all enjoyed the rest of their day, feeling happy and content with each other's company.
